  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Aliment
    Define an Aliment by its attributes Aliment.frequency, Aliment.calories, Aliment.carbohydrates, Aliment.fat, Aliment.milk, Aliment.nuts, Aliment.egg and Aliment.gluten.
    Dish
    Define a Dish with ist attributes MenuElement.getName(), MenuElement.getDescription() extends from de parent class MenuElement and a List<Ingredient>
    Ingredient
    Represents an Ingredient by its attributes Ingredient.quantity and aliments.
    Menu
    Represents a Menu data by its attributes Menu.date and a List<MenuElement> of Menu.elements
    MenuElement
    Abstract class to define a basic elements needed to represent a food Menu by its MenuElement.name, MenuElement.description and abstract methods: MenuElement.getCalories(), MenuElement.getCarbohydrates(), MenuElement.getFat(), MenuElement.isMilk(), MenuElement.isNuts(), MenuElement.isEgg() and MenuElement.isGluten() to be implemented by its subclasses.
